032930%--></li><li class=3D"tocline"><a class=3D"tocxref" href=3D"https://w=
3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#references"><bdi class=3D"secno">B.<!---0.0=
32930%--> </bdi>References<!---0.032930%--></a><!---0.032930%--><ol class=
=3D"toc"><li class=3D"tocline"><a class=3D"tocxref" href=3D"https://w3c.git=
hub.io/mediacapture-main/#normative-references"><bdi class=3D"secno">B.1<!-=
--0.032930%--> </bdi>Normative references<!---0.032930%--></a><!---0.032930=
%--></li><li class=3D"tocline"><a class=3D"tocxref" href=3D"https://w3c.git=
hub.io/mediacapture-main/#informative-references"><bdi class=3D"secno">B.2<=
!---0.032930%--> </bdi>Informative references<!---0.032930%--></a><!---0.03=
