t need to
            be taken into account when trying to garbage collect <a data-xr=
ef-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaStream" href=3D"ht=
tps://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediastream" class=3D"internalDF=
N" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastream-51"><code>MediaStream<!---0.032930%--></co=
