ack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack"=
 class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-34"><code>MediaSt=
reamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--></h3><a class=3D"self=
-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#mediastreamtrack" a=
ria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 4.3"></a></div>
     =20
      <p>A <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"Me=
diaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-medias=
treamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-35"><c=
ode>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> object re=
presents a media
      source in the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w=
3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-user-agent" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D=
"ref-for-dfn-user-agent-11">User Agent<!---0.032930%--></a>. An example sou=
rce is a device connected to the
      <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/m=
ediacapture-main/#dfn-user-agent" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-u=
ser-agent-12">User Agent<!---0.032930%--></a>. Other specifications may def=
ine sources for
      <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSt=
reamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediastream=
track" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-36"><code>M=
ediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> that override =
the behavior specified
      here. Several <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data=
-lt=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#d=
om-mediastreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtra=
ck-37"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> =
objects can represent
      the same media source, e.g., when the user chooses the same camera in=
 the
      UI shown by two consecutive calls to <!---0.032930%--><a data-link-ty=
pe=3D"idl" data-xref-type=3D"method" data-link-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-xr=
ef-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-lt=3D"getUserMedia()" href=3D"https://w3c.gith=
ub.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediadevices-getusermedia" class=3D"internalDF=
N" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediadevices-getusermedia-4"><code>getUserMedia<!---0.=
032930%--></code></a><code>(<!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930=
%-->)</code><!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%-->.</p>
      <p>A <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"Me=
diaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-medias=
treamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-38"><c=
ode>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> source de=
fines the following properties:
        </p><ol>
	  <li>A source has a <dfn data-export=3D"" id=3D"dfn-mediastreamtrack-sour=
ce-type" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">Medi=
aStreamTrack source type</dfn>.
             It is set to either <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=
=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediaca=
pture-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-m=
ediastreamtrack-39"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---=
0.032930%--> or a subtype of <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"=
idl" data-lt=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacaptur=
e-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-media=
streamtrack-40"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.03=
2930%-->.
             By default, it is set to <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link=
-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/me=
diacapture-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-=
dom-mediastreamtrack-41"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a>=
<!---0.032930%-->. </li>
          <li>A source has <dfn data-export=3D"" id=3D"dfn-mediastreamtrack=
-source-specific-construction-steps" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog=
" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">MediaStreamTrack source-specific construction steps=
</dfn>
            that are executed when creating a <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" d=
ata-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.gith=
ub.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"=
ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-42"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></c=
ode></a><!---0.032930%--> from a source.
            The steps take a newly created <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data=
-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.=
io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref=
-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-43"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code=
></a><!---0.032930%--> as input. By default, the steps are empty.</li>
          <li>A source has <dfn data-export=3D"" id=3D"dfn-mediastreamtrack=
-source-specific-clone-steps" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-=
dfn-type=3D"dfn">MediaStreamTrack source-specific clone steps</dfn>
            that are executed when cloning a <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" da=
ta-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.githu=
b.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"r=
ef-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-44"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></co=
de></a><!---0.032930%--> of the given source.
            The steps take the source and destination <a data-xref-type=3D"=
_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://=
w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN=
" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-45"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.03293=
0%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->s as input. By default, the steps are empt=
y.</li>
        </ol>
      <p></p>

      <p>The data from a <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl"=
 data-lt=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-ma=
in/#dom-mediastreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastre=
amtrack-46"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930=
%--> object does not
      necessarily have a canonical binary form; for example, it could just =
be
      "the video currently coming from the user's video camera". This allow=
s
      <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/m=
ediacapture-main/#dfn-user-agent" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-u=
ser-agent-13">User Agents<!---0.032930%--></a> to manipulate media in whate=
ver fashion is most suitable on
      the user's platform.</p>
      <p>A script can indicate that a <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link=
-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/me=
diacapture-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-=
dom-mediastreamtrack-47"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a>=
<!---0.032930%-->
      object no longer needs its source with the <!---0.032930%--><a data-l=
ink-type=3D"idl" data-xref-type=3D"method" data-link-for=3D"MediaStreamTrac=
k" data-xref-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-lt=3D"stop()" href=3D"https://w3=
c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack-stop" class=3D"internal=
DFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-stop-1"><code>stop<!---0.032930%-->=
</code></a><code>(<!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%-->)</cod=
e><!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%-->
      method. When all tracks
      using a source have been stopped or ended by some other means, the so=
urce
      is <dfn id=3D"source-stopped" data-lt=3D"source stopped state|stopped=
" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">stopped</df=
n>. If the source is a device
      exposed by <!---0.032930%--><a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-xref-type=
=3D"method" data-link-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-xref-for=3D"MediaDevices" d=
ata-lt=3D"getUserMedia()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#=
dom-mediadevices-getusermedia" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-medi=
adevices-getusermedia-5"><code>getUserMedia<!---0.032930%--></code></a><cod=
e>(<!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%-->)</code><!---0.032930=
%--><!---0.032930%-->, then when
      the source is stopped, the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-user-agent" class=3D"inter=
nalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-user-agent-14">User Agent<!---0.032930%--></a> <e=
m class=3D"rfc2119">MUST<!---0.032930%--></em> run the following steps:</p>
      <ol class=3D"algorithm">
        <li>
          <p>Let <var>mediaDevices</var> be the <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_"=
 data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaDevices" href=3D"https://w3c.github=
.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediadevices" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-fo=
r-dom-mediadevices-1"><code>MediaDevices<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.=
032930%--> object in question.</p>
        </li><li>
          <p>Let <var>deviceId</var> be the source device's <!---0.032930%-=
-><a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-xref-type=3D"attribute|dict-member|const" =
data-link-for=3D"MediaDeviceInfo" data-xref-for=3D"MediaDeviceInfo" href=3D=
"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediadeviceinfo-deviceid" cla=
ss=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediadeviceinfo-deviceid-1"><code>devi=
ceId<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>Set <var>mediaDevices</var>.<!---0.032930%--><a data-xref-type=
=3D"attribute" data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-link-for=3D"MediaDevices" =
data-xref-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-lt=3D"[[devicesLiveMap]]" href=3D"https=
://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-deviceslivemap" class=3D"internalDF=
N" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-deviceslivemap-1"><code>[[devicesLiveMap<!---0.032930%=
-->]]<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->[<var>deviceId</var>] to
          <code>false</code>.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>If the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=3D"permissions" dat=
a-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"dfn-permission-state" href=3D"https://ww=
w.w3.org/TR/permissions/#dfn-permission-state">permission state<!---0.03293=
0%--></a>
          of the permission associated with the device's kind and
          <var>deviceId</var> for <var>mediaDevices</var>'s <a data-link-ty=
pe=3D"dfn" data-cite=3D"html" data-cite-path=3D"/webappapis.html" data-cite=
-frag=3D"relevant-settings-object" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/mul=
tipage/webappapis.html#relevant-settings-object">relevant settings object<!=
---0.032930%--></a>,
          is not "<a data-link-type=3D"enum-value" data-xref-type=3D"enum-v=
alue" data-link-for=3D"PermissionState" data-xref-for=3D"PermissionState" d=
ata-cite=3D"permissions" data-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"dom-permissi=
onstate-granted" href=3D"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions/#dom-permissions=
tate-granted"><code>granted<!---0.032930%--></code></a>"<!---0.032930%-->, =
then set
          <var>mediaDevices</var>.<!---0.032930%--><a data-xref-type=3D"att=
ribute" data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-link-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-xr=
ef-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-lt=3D"[[devicesAccessibleMap]]" href=3D"https:=
//w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-devicesaccessiblemap" class=3D"inter=
nalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-devicesaccessiblemap-1"><code>[[devicesAccessible=
Map<!---0.032930%-->]]<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->[<var>de=
viceId</var>] to
          <code>false</code>.</p>
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>To <dfn class=3D"abstract-op" data-dfn-type=3D"abstract-op" id=3D"=
dfn-create-a-mediastreamtrack" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data=
-export=3D"">create a MediaStreamTrack</dfn> with an underlying
      <var>source</var>, and a <var>mediaDevicesToTieSourceTo</var>, run th=
e
      following steps:</p>
      <ol class=3D"algorithm">
        <li>
          <p>Let <var>track</var> be a new object of type <var>source</var>=
's <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/medi=
acapture-main/#dfn-mediastreamtrack-source-type" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dfn-mediastreamtrack-source-type-1">MediaStreamTrack source typ=
e<!---0.032930%--></a>.</p>
          <p>Initialize track with the following internal slots:</p>
          <ul data-dfn-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack">
            <li>
              <p><dfn data-idl=3D"" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-=
noexport=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dfn-source-0" tabindex=3D"0=
" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog">[[Source]]</dfn>,
              initialized to <var>source</var>.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p><dfn data-idl=3D"" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-=
noexport=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dfn-id" tabindex=3D"0" aria=
-haspopup=3D"dialog">[[Id]]</dfn>,
              initialized to a newly generated unique identifier string. Se=
e
              <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D=
"MediaStream" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediastr=
eam" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastream-52"><code>MediaStr=
eam<!---0.032930%--></code></a>.<!---0.032930%--><a data-link-type=3D"idl" =
data-xref-type=3D"attribute|dict-member|const" data-link-for=3D"MediaStream=
" data-xref-for=3D"MediaStream" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-=
main/#dom-mediastream-id" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastre=
am-id-6"><code>id<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> attribute fo=
r guidelines on how to generate
              such an identifier.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p><dfn data-idl=3D"" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-=
noexport=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dfn-kind" tabindex=3D"0" ar=
ia-haspopup=3D"dialog">[[Kind]]</dfn>,
              initialized to <dfn id=3D"dfn-audio" tabindex=3D"0" aria-hasp=
opup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn"><code>"audio"</code></dfn> if <var>so=
urce</var> is
              an audio source, or <dfn id=3D"dfn-video" tabindex=3D"0" aria=
-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn"><code>"video"</code></dfn> if
              <var>source</var> is a video source.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p><dfn data-idl=3D"" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-=
noexport=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dfn-label" tabindex=3D"0" a=
ria-haspopup=3D"dialog">[[Label]]</dfn>,
              initialized to <var>source</var>'s label, if provided by the =
User
              Agent, or <code>""</code> otherwise. <a data-link-type=3D"dfn=
|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-user-age=
nt" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-user-agent-15">User Agents<!---=
0.032930%--></a> <em class=3D"rfc2119">MAY<!---0.032930%--></em> label audi=
o and
              video sources (e.g., "Internal microphone" or "External USB W=
ebcam").
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p><dfn data-idl=3D"" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-=
noexport=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dfn-readystate" tabindex=3D=
"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog">[[ReadyState]]</dfn>,
              initialized to "<a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-xref-type=3D"e=
num-value" data-link-for=3D"MediaStreamTrackState" data-xref-for=3D"MediaSt=
reamTrackState" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#idl-def-Me=
diaStreamTrackState.live" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-idl-def-Media=
StreamTrackState.live-1"><code>live<!---0.032930%--></code></a>"<!---0.0329=
30%-->.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p><dfn data-idl=3D"" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-=
noexport=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dfn-enabled" tabindex=3D"0"=
 aria-haspopup=3D"dialog">[[Enabled]]</dfn>,
              initialized to <code>true</code>.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p><dfn data-idl=3D"" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-=
noexport=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dfn-muted" tabindex=3D"0" a=
ria-haspopup=3D"dialog">[[Muted]]</dfn>,
              initialized to <code>true</code> if <var>source</var> is
              <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" data-link-for=3D"source=
" data-xref-for=3D"source" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/=
#dfn-muted-0" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-muted-0-1">muted<!---=
0.032930%--></a>, and <code>false</code> otherwise.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a data-link-for=3D"constrainable object" data-link-type=3D"a=
ttribute" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-capabilities=
-0" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-capabilities-0-1">[[Capabilitie=
s]]</a>,
              <a data-link-for=3D"constrainable object" data-link-type=3D"a=
ttribute" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-constraints"=
 class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-constraints-1">[[Constraints]]</a>=
, and
              <a data-link-for=3D"constrainable object" data-link-type=3D"a=
ttribute" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-settings-0" =
class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-settings-0-1">[[Settings]]</a>, all=
 initialized as
              specified in the <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=
=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"ConstrainablePattern" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/med=
iacapture-main/#dom-constrainablepattern" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-f=
or-dom-constrainablepattern-5"><code>ConstrainablePattern<!---0.032930%--><=
/code></a><!---0.032930%-->.<p></p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p><dfn class=3D"export" data-idl=3D"" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaS=
treamTrack" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" data-export=3D"" id=3D"dfn-restrict=
able" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog">[[Restrictable]]</dfn>, initi=
alized to <code>false</code>.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>If <var>mediaDevicesToTieSourceTo</var> is not <code>null</cod=
e>,
          <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.=
io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-tie-track-source-to-mediadevices" class=3D"intern=
alDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-tie-track-source-to-mediadevices-1">tie track sour=
ce to <code>MediaDevices<!---0.032930%--></code><!---0.032930%--></a> with =
<var>source</var> and <var>mediaDevicesToTieSourceTo</var>.</p>
        </li>
        <li><p>Run <var>source</var>'s <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op=
" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-mediastreamtrack-sou=
rce-specific-construction-steps" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-me=
diastreamtrack-source-specific-construction-steps-1">MediaStreamTrack sourc=
e-specific construction steps<!---0.032930%--></a>
