arlier
        should it detect a device problem, like the device being physically
        removed).</p>
        <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-generatedID=
-2"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note-2" aria-=
level=3D"6"><span>Note</span><!---0.032930%--></div><div class=3D"">
          <p>The intent is to give users the assurance of privacy that havi=
ng
          physical camera (and microphone) hardware lights off brings, by
          aligning physical and logical =E2=80=9Cprivacy indicators=E2=80=
=9D, at least while the
          current document is the sole user of a device.</p>
          <p>While other applications and documents using the device
          simultaneously may interfere with this intent at times, they do n=
ot
          interfere with the rules laid forth.</p>
        </div></div>
        <p>A <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"=
MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-medi=
astreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-63">=
<code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> object =
is said to
        <em>end</em> when the source of the track is disconnected or
        exhausted.</p>
        <p>If all <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-l=
t=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom=
-mediastreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack=
-64"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->s t=
hat are using the same
        source are <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" data-link-for=3D"M=
ediaStreamTrack" data-xref-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.git=
hub.io/mediacapture-main/#track-ended" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-=
track-ended-5">ended<!---0.032930%--></a>, the source will be
        <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" data-link-for=3D"source" data=
-xref-for=3D"source" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#sourc=
e-stopped" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-source-stopped-2">stopped<!-=
--0.032930%--></a>.</p>
        <p>After the application has invoked the <!---0.032930%--><a data-l=
ink-type=3D"idl" data-xref-type=3D"method" data-link-for=3D"MediaStreamTrac=
k" data-xref-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-lt=3D"stop()" href=3D"https://w3=
c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack-stop" class=3D"internal=
