</code></a><code>(<!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%-->)</cod=
e><!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%-->
        method on a <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data=
-lt=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#d=
om-mediastreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtra=
ck-65"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> =
object, or once the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w=
3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-source" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref=
-for-dfn-source-3">source<!---0.032930%--></a> of a
