amtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-66"><code=
>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> permanently =
ends production of live samples to its tracks,
        whichever is sooner, a <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=
=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediaca=
pture-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-m=
ediastreamtrack-67"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---=
0.032930%--> is said to be
        <dfn id=3D"track-ended" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-dfn-=
type=3D"dfn" data-export=3D"" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog">ended=
</dfn>.</p>
        <p>For camera and microphone sources, the reasons for a source to
        <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" data-link-for=3D"MediaStreamT=
rack" data-xref-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-lt=3D"ended" href=3D"https://=
w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#track-ended" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"r=
ef-for-track-ended-6">end<!---0.032930%--></a> besides <!---0.032930%--><a =
data-link-type=3D"idl" data-xref-type=3D"method" data-link-for=3D"MediaStre=
amTrack" data-xref-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-lt=3D"stop()" href=3D"http=
s://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack-stop" class=3D"in=
ternalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-stop-3"><code>stop<!---0.0329=
30%--></code></a><code>(<!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%-->=
)</code><!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%--> are
         <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=3D"infra" data-cite-path=3D"" =
data-cite-frag=3D"implementation-defined" href=3D"https://infra.spec.whatwg=
.org/#implementation-defined">implementation-defined<!---0.032930%--></a>
        (e.g., because the user rescinds the permission for the page to
        use the local camera, or because the User
        Agent has instructed the track to end for any reason).</p>
        <p>When a <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-l=
t=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom=
-mediastreamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack=
-68"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> <v=
ar>track</var>
        <dfn data-lt=3D"track ended by the User agent|ends for any reason o=
ther than the stop() method being invoked" data-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" da=
ta-export=3D"" id=3D"ends-nostop" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" d=
ata-dfn-type=3D"dfn">ends for any reason other than the <code>stop()<!---0.=
