" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-user-agent-25">User Agent<!---0.032930%--></a> <em clas=
s=3D"rfc2119">MUST<!---0.032930%--></em> queue a task that runs the followi=
ng
        steps:</p>
        <ol class=3D"algorithm">
