mTrackState" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#idl-def-Media=
StreamTrackState.ended" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-idl-def-MediaSt=
reamTrackState.ended-2"><code>ended<!---0.032930%--></code></a>"<!---0.0329=
30%--> already, then abort these
            steps.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Set <var>track</var>'s <!---0.032930%--><a data-xref-type=3D=
"attribute" data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-link-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack"=
 data-xref-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-lt=3D"[[ReadyState]]" href=3D"http=
s://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-readystate" class=3D"internalDFN" =
id=3D"ref-for-dfn-readystate-5"><code>[[ReadyState<!---0.032930%-->]]<!---0=
.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->
            to "<a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-xref-type=3D"enum-value" dat=
a-link-for=3D"MediaStreamTrackState" data-xref-for=3D"MediaStreamTrackState=
" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#idl-def-MediaStreamTrack=
State.ended" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-idl-def-MediaStreamTrackSt=
ate.ended-3"><code>ended<!---0.032930%--></code></a>"<!---0.032930%-->.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Notify <var>track</var>'s <!---0.032930%--><a data-xref-type=
=3D"attribute" data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-link-for=3D"MediaStreamTra=
ck" data-xref-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-lt=3D"[[Source]]" href=3D"https=
://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-source-0" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dfn-source-0-3"><code>[[Source<!---0.032930%-->]]<!---0.032930%=
