       =20
        <p><a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"Me=
diaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-medias=
treamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-70"><c=
ode>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> is a <a h=
