88"><code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->. It=
 conforms with the definition of
                <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=
=3D"MediaDeviceInfo" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-m=
