>assigned media provider object</a>, the attributes listed will appear to
    resume the values they had before a stream was assigned to the element.=
</p>
    <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-generatedID-13"=
><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note-13" aria-le=
