=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#dom-media-playbackrat=
e"><code>playbackRate<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->
      and <!---0.032930%--><a data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-xref-type=
=3D"attribute|dict-member|const" data-link-for=3D"HTMLMediaElement" data-xr=
ef-for=3D"HTMLMediaElement" data-cite=3D"html" data-cite-path=3D"/media.htm=
l" data-cite-frag=3D"dom-media-defaultplaybackrate" href=3D"https://html.sp=
ec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#dom-media-defaultplaybackrate"><code>def=
aultPlaybackRate<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> were differen=
