=3D"" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog"><code>MediaDevices</code></df=
n> object is the entry point
      to the API used to examine and get access to media devices available =
to
      the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.=
io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-user-agent" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-d=
fn-user-agent-48">User Agent<!---0.032930%--></a>.</p>
      <p>To <dfn class=3D"abstract-op" data-dfn-type=3D"abstract-op" id=3D"=
