port=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dfn-kindsaccessiblemap" tabinde=
x=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog">[[kindsAccessibleMap]]</dfn>,
               initialized to an empty <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-lt=3D=
"ordered map" data-cite=3D"infra" data-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"ord=
ered-map" href=3D"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#ordered-map">map<!---0.032=
930%--></a>.</p>
