port=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dfn-canexposemicrophoneinfo" ta=
bindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog">[[canExposeMicrophoneInfo]]</dfn>, in=
itialized
              to <code>false</code>.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p><dfn data-dfn-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-idl=3D"" data-noex=
port=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dfn-mediastreamtracksources" ta=
