=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"devicechange" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacaptur=
e-main/#event-mediadevices-devicechange" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-fo=
r-event-mediadevices-devicechange-2"><code>devicechange<!---0.032930%--></c=
ode></a><!---0.032930%-->,
          using the <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data=
-lt=3D"DeviceChangeEvent" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#=
dom-devicechangeevent" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-devicechange=
event-2"><code>DeviceChangeEvent<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-=
-> constructor with <!---0.032930%--><a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-xref-ty=
pe=3D"attribute|dict-member|const" data-link-for=3D"DeviceChangeEventInit" =
data-xref-for=3D"DeviceChangeEventInit" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/media=
capture-main/#dom-devicechangeeventinit-devices" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dom-devicechangeeventinit-devices-1"><code>devices<!---0.032930=
%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->
          initialized to <var>newExposedDevices</var>, at <var>mediaDevices=
</var>.</p>
          <p>The <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.=
github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-user-agent" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"re=
f-for-dfn-user-agent-53">User Agent<!---0.032930%--></a> <em class=3D"rfc21=
19">MAY<!---0.032930%--></em> combine firing multiple events into firing on=
e
          event when several events are due or when multiple devices are ad=
ded
          or removed at the same time, e.g. a camera with a microphone.</p>
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>Additionally, if a <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"i=
dl" data-lt=3D"MediaDevices" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-mai=
n/#dom-mediadevices" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediadevices-1=
4"><code>MediaDevices<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> object t=
hat was traversed comes
      to meet the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c=
.github.io/mediacapture-main/#device-enumeration-can-proceed" class=3D"inte=
rnalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-device-enumeration-can-proceed-2">device enumeration=
 can proceed<!---0.032930%--></a> criteria later (e.g.
      <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" data-link-for=3D"Document" data=
-xref-for=3D"Document" data-lt=3D"is in view" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io=
/mediacapture-main/#dfn-is-in-view" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn=
-is-in-view-4">comes into view<!---0.032930%--></a>), the <a data-link-type=
=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-u=
ser-agent" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-user-agent-54">User Agen=
t<!---0.032930%--></a> <em class=3D"rfc2119">MUST<!---0.032930%--></em>
      execute the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c=
.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-device-change-notification-steps" class=
=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-device-change-notification-steps-1">devi=
ce change notification steps<!---0.032930%--></a> on the <a data-xref-type=
=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaDevices" href=3D"https://=
w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediadevices" class=3D"internalDFN" id=
=3D"ref-for-dom-mediadevices-15"><code>MediaDevices<!---0.032930%--></code>=
</a><!---0.032930%-->
      object at that time.</p>
      <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-generatedID-1=
6"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note-16" aria-=
level=3D"4"><span>Note</span><!---0.032930%--></div><div class=3D"">
        <p class=3D"fingerprint">These events are potentially triggered
        simultaneously on documents of different origins. <a data-link-type=
=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-u=
ser-agent" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-user-agent-55">User Agen=
ts<!---0.032930%--></a> <em class=3D"rfc2119">MAY<!---0.032930%--></em> add
        fuzzing on the timing of events to avoid cross-origin activity
        correlation.<img src=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/ima=
ges/fingerprint.png" alt=3D"(This is a fingerprinting vector.)" width=3D"15=
" height=3D"21"></p>
      </div></div>
