          <dl data-link-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaDevices" =
class=3D"attributes">
            <dt><dfn data-export=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"attribute" id=3D"dom=
-mediadevices-ondevicechange" data-idl=3D"attribute" data-title=3D"ondevice=
change" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-type=3D"EventHandler" data-lt=3D=
"ondevicechange" data-local-lt=3D"MediaDevices.ondevicechange" tabindex=3D"=
0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog"><code>ondevicechange</code></dfn> of type <a da=
ta-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"typedef" data-lt=3D"EventHandler" =
data-cite=3D"html" data-cite-path=3D"/webappapis.html" data-cite-frag=3D"ev=
enthandler" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#=
eventhandler"><code>EventHandler<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-=
-></dt>
            <dd>
              <p>The event type of this event handler is <a data-link-type=
=3D"event" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#event-mediadevi=
ces-devicechange" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-event-mediadevices-de=
vicechange-3">devicechange</a>.</p>
            </dd>
