        </section>
        <section>
          <div class=3D"header-wrapper"><h4 id=3D"methods-1">Methods</h4><a=
 class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#metho=
ds-1" aria-label=3D"Permalink for this Section"></a></div>
          <dl data-link-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaDevices" =
class=3D"methods">
            <dt><dfn data-export=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"method" id=3D"dom-me=
diadevices-enumeratedevices" data-idl=3D"operation" data-title=3D"enumerate=
Devices" data-dfn-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-type=3D"Promise" data-lt=3D"enu=
merateDevices()" data-local-lt=3D"MediaDevices.enumerateDevices|MediaDevice=
s.enumerateDevices()|enumerateDevices" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dial=
og"><code>enumerateDevices</code></dfn></dt>
            <dd>
              <p>Collects information about the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|ab=
stract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-user-agent"=
 class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-user-agent-56">User Agent<!---0.03=
2930%--></a>'s available media
              input and output devices.</p>
              <p>This method returns a promise. The promise will be
              <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-lt=3D"upon fulfillment" data-c=
ite=3D"webidl" data-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"upon-fulfillment" href=
=3D"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#upon-fulfillment">fulfilled<!---0.03293=
0%--></a> with a sequence of
              <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D=
"MediaDeviceInfo" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-medi=
adeviceinfo" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediadeviceinfo-5"><co=
de>MediaDeviceInfo<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> objects rep=
resenting the
              <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.git=
hub.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-user-agent" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-f=
or-dfn-user-agent-57">User Agent<!---0.032930%--></a>'s available media inp=
ut and output devices if
              enumeration is successful.</p>
              <p>Elements of this sequence that represent input devices wil=
l be
              of type <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" da=
ta-lt=3D"InputDeviceInfo" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#=
dom-inputdeviceinfo" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-inputdeviceinf=
o-1"><code>InputDeviceInfo<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> whi=
ch extends
              <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D=
"MediaDeviceInfo" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-medi=
adeviceinfo" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediadeviceinfo-6"><co=
de>MediaDeviceInfo<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->.</p>
              <p>Camera and microphone sources <em class=3D"rfc2119">SHOULD=
<!---0.032930%--></em>
              be enumerable. Specifications that add additional types of so=
urce
              will provide recommendations about whether the source type sh=
ould
              be enumerable.</p>
              <p>When the <!---0.032930%--><a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-x=
ref-type=3D"method" data-link-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-xref-for=3D"MediaDe=
vices" data-lt=3D"enumerateDevices()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediaca=
pture-main/#dom-mediadevices-enumeratedevices" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"=
ref-for-dom-mediadevices-enumeratedevices-4"><code>enumerateDevices<!---0.0=
32930%--></code></a><code>(<!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%=
-->)</code><!---0.032930%--><!---0.032930%--> method is
              called, the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"htt=
ps://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-user-agent" class=3D"internalDFN"=
 id=3D"ref-for-dfn-user-agent-58">User Agent<!---0.032930%--></a> must run =
the following steps:</p>
              <ol class=3D"algorithm">
                <li>
                  <p>Let <var>p</var> be a new promise.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <p>Let <var>proceed</var> be the result of
                  <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c=
.github.io/mediacapture-main/#device-enumeration-can-proceed" class=3D"inte=
rnalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-device-enumeration-can-proceed-3">device enumeration=
 can proceed<!---0.032930%--></a> with <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=
=3D"webidl" data-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"this" href=3D"https://web=
idl.spec.whatwg.org/#this">this<!---0.032930%--></a>.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <p>Let <var>mediaDevices</var> be <a data-link-type=3D"df=
n" data-cite=3D"webidl" data-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"this" href=3D=
"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this">this<!---0.032930%--></a>.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <p>Run the following steps in parallel:</p>
                  <ol>
                    <li>
                      <p>While <var>proceed</var> is <code>false<!---0.0329=
30%--></code>, the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3=
c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-user-agent" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"=
ref-for-dfn-user-agent-59">User Agent<!---0.032930%--></a>
                      <em class=3D"rfc2119">MUST<!---0.032930%--></em> wait=
 to proceed to the next step until a task queued
                      to set <var>proceed</var> to the result of
                      <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https:/=
/w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#device-enumeration-can-proceed" class=3D"=
internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-device-enumeration-can-proceed-4">device enumera=
tion can proceed<!---0.032930%--></a> with <var>mediaDevices</var>, would s=
et
                      <var>proceed</var> to <code>true<!---0.032930%--></co=
de>.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <p>Let <var>resultList</var> be the result of
                      <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https:/=
/w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#creating-a-list-of-device-info-objects" c=
lass=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-creating-a-list-of-device-info-objects-3=
">creating a list of device info objects<!---0.032930%--></a> with <var>med=
iaDevices</var> and
                      <var>mediaDevices</var>.<!---0.032930%--><a data-xref=
-type=3D"attribute" data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-link-for=3D"MediaDevi=
ces" data-xref-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-lt=3D"[[storedDeviceList]]" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-storeddevicelist" class=3D=
"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-storeddevicelist-3"><code>[[storedDeviceLis=
t<!---0.032930%-->]]<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->.</p></li>
                    <li>
                      <p><a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=3D"webidl" dat=
a-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"resolve" href=3D"https://webidl.spec.wha=
twg.org/#resolve">resolve<!---0.032930%--></a> <var>p</var> with <var>resul=
tList</var>.</p>
                    </li>
                  </ol>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <p>Return <var>p</var>.</p>
                </li>
              </ol>
              <p>To perform
              <dfn class=3D"abstract-op" id=3D"creating-a-list-of-device-in=
fo-objects" data-dfn-type=3D"abstract-op" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"d=
ialog" data-export=3D"">
              creating a list of device info objects</dfn>, given
              <var>mediaDevices</var> and <var>deviceList</var>,
              run the following steps:</p>
              <ol class=3D"algorithm">
                <li><p>Let <var>resultList</var> be an empty list.</p></li>
                <li>
                  <p>Let <var>microphoneList</var>, <var>cameraList</var> a=
nd <var>otherDeviceList</var> be empty lists.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <p>Let <var>document</var> be <var>mediaDevices</var>'s
                  <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=3D"html" data-cite-pa=
th=3D"/webappapis.html" data-cite-frag=3D"concept-relevant-global" href=3D"=
https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-glo=
bal">relevant global object<!---0.032930%--></a>'s <a data-link-type=3D"dfn=
" data-cite=3D"html" data-cite-path=3D"/nav-history-apis.html" data-cite-fr=
ag=3D"concept-document-window" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipa=
ge/nav-history-apis.html#concept-document-window">associated <code>Document=
<!---0.032930%--></code><!---0.032930%--></a>.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <p>Run the following sub steps for each discovered device=
 in <var>deviceList</var>, <var>device</var>:</p>
                  <ol>
                    <li>
                      <p>If <var>device</var> is not a microphone, or <var>=
document</var> is not
                      <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=3D"html" data-cit=
e-path=3D"/iframe-embed-object.html" data-cite-frag=3D"allowed-to-use" href=
=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/iframe-embed-object.html#allowed=
-to-use">allowed to use<!---0.032930%--></a> the feature identified by <a h=
ref=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-microphone" class=3D"in=
ternalDFN" data-link-type=3D"dfn" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-microphone-3"><code>"mi=
crophone"</code></a>,
                      abort these sub steps and continue with the next devi=
ce (if any).</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <p>Let <var>deviceInfo</var> be the result of
                      <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https:/=
/w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#creating-a-device-info-object" class=3D"i=
