xposure" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 9.2.2"></a></div>
       =20
        <p>To perform a <dfn class=3D"abstract-op" id=3D"device-enumeration=
-can-proceed" data-dfn-type=3D"abstract-op" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D=
"dialog" data-export=3D"">device enumeration can proceed</dfn> check, given=
 <var>mediaDevices</var>,
        run the following steps:</p>
        <ol class=3D"algorithm">
          <li>
            <p>The <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3=
c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-user-agent" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"=
ref-for-dfn-user-agent-63">User Agent<!---0.032930%--></a> <em class=3D"rfc=
2119">MAY<!---0.032930%--></em> return <code>true</code> if
