lDFN" id=3D"ref-for-device-information-can-be-exposed-1">device information=
 can be exposed<!---0.032930%--></a> on <var>mediaDevices</var>.
          </p></li>
          <li>
            <p>Return the result of <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" d=
ata-link-for=3D"Document" data-xref-for=3D"Document" href=3D"https://w3c.gi=
thub.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-is-in-view" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-=
for-dfn-is-in-view-5">is in view<!---0.032930%--></a> with <var>mediaDevice=
s</var>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
        <p>To perform a <dfn class=3D"abstract-op" id=3D"device-information=
-can-be-exposed" data-dfn-type=3D"abstract-op" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=
=3D"dialog" data-export=3D"">device information can be exposed</dfn>
        check, given <var>mediaDevices</var>, run the following steps:</p>
        <ol class=3D"algorithm">
          <li>
            <p>If <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c=
.github.io/mediacapture-main/#camera-information-can-be-exposed" class=3D"i=
nternalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-camera-information-can-be-exposed-3">camera infor=
mation can be exposed<!---0.032930%--></a> on <var>mediaDevices</var>,
            return <code>true</code>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>If <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c=
.github.io/mediacapture-main/#microphone-information-can-be-exposed" class=
=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-microphone-information-can-be-exposed-3">mic=
rophone information can be exposed<!---0.032930%--></a> on <var>mediaDevice=
s</var>,
            return <code>true</code>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Return <code>false</code>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
        <p>To perform a <dfn class=3D"abstract-op" id=3D"camera-information=
-can-be-exposed" data-dfn-type=3D"abstract-op" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=
=3D"dialog" data-export=3D"">camera information can be exposed</dfn>
        check, given <var>mediaDevices</var>, run the following steps:</p>
