            <p>If any of the local devices of kind "videoinput" are attache=
d to a live
            <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"M=
ediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-media=
streamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-112">=
<code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> in <var=
>mediaDevices</var>'s <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=3D"html" data-cit=
e-path=3D"/webappapis.html" data-cite-frag=3D"concept-relevant-global" href=
=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant=
-global">relevant global object<!---0.032930%--></a>'s
            <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=3D"html" data-cite-path=3D"=
/nav-history-apis.html" data-cite-frag=3D"concept-document-window" href=3D"=
https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-docume=
nt-window">associated <code>Document<!---0.032930%--></code><!---0.032930%-=
