f=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-canexposecamerainfo" clas=
s=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-canexposecamerainfo-1"><code>[[canExpos=
eCameraInfo<!---0.032930%-->]]<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->=
.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
        <p>To perform a <dfn class=3D"abstract-op" id=3D"microphone-informa=
tion-can-be-exposed" data-dfn-type=3D"abstract-op" tabindex=3D"0" aria-hasp=
opup=3D"dialog" data-export=3D"">microphone information can be exposed</dfn=
>
        check, given <var>mediaDevices</var>, run the following steps:</p>
        <ol class=3D"algorithm">
          <li>
            <p>If any of the local devices of kind "audioinput" are attache=
d to a live
            <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"M=
ediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-media=
streamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-113">=
<code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> in the =
<a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=3D"html" data-cite-path=3D"/webappapis.=
html" data-cite-frag=3D"concept-relevant-global" href=3D"https://html.spec.=
whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global">relevant glob=
al object<!---0.032930%--></a>'s
            <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=3D"html" data-cite-path=3D"=
/nav-history-apis.html" data-cite-frag=3D"concept-document-window" href=3D"=
https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-docume=
nt-window">associated <code>Document<!---0.032930%--></code><!---0.032930%-=
-></a>, return <code>true</code>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Return <var>mediaDevices</var>.<!---0.032930%--><a data-xref=
-type=3D"attribute" data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-link-for=3D"MediaDevi=
ces" data-xref-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-lt=3D"[[canExposeMicrophoneInfo]]"=
 href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-canexposemicrophonein=
fo" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-canexposemicrophoneinfo-1"><cod=
e>[[canExposeMicrophoneInfo<!---0.032930%-->]]<!---0.032930%--></code></a><=
!---0.032930%-->.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
        <p>To perform an <dfn data-dfn-for=3D"Document" class=3D"abstract-o=
p" data-dfn-type=3D"abstract-op" id=3D"dfn-is-in-view" tabindex=3D"0" aria-=
haspopup=3D"dialog" data-export=3D"">is in view</dfn> check, given <var>med=
iaDevices</var>, run the following
        steps:</p>
        <ol class=3D"algorithm">
          <li>
            <p>If <var>mediaDevices</var>'s <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-=
cite=3D"html" data-cite-path=3D"/webappapis.html" data-cite-frag=3D"concept=
-relevant-global" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis=
.html#concept-relevant-global">relevant global object<!---0.032930%--></a>'=
s <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=3D"html" data-cite-path=3D"/nav-histo=
ry-apis.html" data-cite-frag=3D"concept-document-window" href=3D"https://ht=
ml.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-document-window"=
>associated <code>Document<!---0.032930%--></code><!---0.032930%--></a> is
            <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-link-for=3D"Document" data-xref-=
for=3D"Document" data-cite=3D"html" data-cite-path=3D"/document-sequences.h=
tml" data-cite-frag=3D"fully-active" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/m=
ultipage/document-sequences.html#fully-active">fully active<!---0.032930%--=
></a> and its <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-link-for=3D"Document" data-xre=
f-for=3D"Document" data-cite=3D"html" data-cite-path=3D"/interaction.html" =
data-cite-frag=3D"visibility-state" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/mu=
ltipage/interaction.html#visibility-state">visibility state<!---0.032930%--=
></a>
            is <code>"visible"<!---0.032930%--></code>, return <code>true<!=
---0.032930%--></code>. Otherwise, return <code>false<!---0.032930%--></cod=
