        </ol>
        <p>To perform a <dfn id=3D"dfn-has-system-focus" tabindex=3D"0" ari=
a-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">has system focus</dfn> check, g=
iven <var>mediaDevices</var>, run the following
        steps:</p>
        <ol class=3D"algorithm">
          <li>
            <p>If <var>mediaDevices</var>'s <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-=
cite=3D"html" data-cite-path=3D"/webappapis.html" data-cite-frag=3D"concept=
-relevant-global" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis=
.html#concept-relevant-global">relevant global object<!---0.032930%--></a>'=
s <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=3D"html" data-cite-path=3D"/document-=
sequences.html" data-cite-frag=3D"navigable" href=3D"https://html.spec.what=
wg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#navigable">navigable<!---0.032930%=
