se<!---0.032930%--></code>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
        <p>To perform a <dfn id=3D"dfn-device-exposure-can-be-extended" tab=
index=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"dfn">device exposure =
can be extended</dfn> check, given <var>deviceType</var>, run the following
        steps:</p>
