      <section id=3D"exposure-decision-algorithm-for-devices-other-than-cam=
era-and-microphone"><div class=3D"header-wrapper"><h4 id=3D"x9-2-4-exposure=
-decision-algorithm-for-devices-other-than-camera-and-microphone"><bdi clas=
s=3D"secno">9.2.4<!---0.032930%--> </bdi>Exposure decision algorithm for de=
vices other than camera and microphone</h4><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"h=
ttps://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#exposure-decision-algorithm-for-dev=
ices-other-than-camera-and-microphone" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section =
9.2.4"></a></div>
       =20
        <p>The <dfn data-export=3D"" id=3D"device-exposure-decision-non-cam=
era-microphone" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" data-dfn-type=3D"df=
n">exposure decision algorithm for devices other than camera and microphone=
</dfn>
          takes a <var>device</var>, <var>microphoneList</var>, <var>camera=
List</var> and
          <var>mediaDevices</var> as input and returns a boolean to decide =
whether to expose
          information about <var>device</var> to the web page or not.</p>
        <p>By default, it returns <code>false</code>.</p>
        <p>Other specifications can define the algorithm for specific devic=
e types.
      </p></section>
      <section id=3D"context-capturing-state"><div class=3D"header-wrapper"=
><h4 id=3D"x9-2-5-context-capturing-state"><bdi class=3D"secno">9.2.5<!---0=
.032930%--> </bdi>Context capturing state</h4><a class=3D"self-link" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#context-capturing-state" aria-=
label=3D"Permalink for Section 9.2.5"></a></div>
       =20
        <p>To perform a <dfn class=3D"abstract-op" id=3D"context-is-capturi=
ng" data-dfn-type=3D"abstract-op" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" d=
ata-export=3D"">context is capturing</dfn> check
        for <var>globalObject</var>, run the following steps:</p>
        <ol class=3D"algorithm">
          <li>
            <p>If <var>globalObject</var> is not a <a data-xref-type=3D"_ID=
L_" data-link-type=3D"interface" data-lt=3D"Window" data-cite=3D"html" data=
-cite-path=3D"/nav-history-apis.html" data-cite-frag=3D"window" href=3D"htt=
ps://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#window"><code>Win=
dow<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->, then return false.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Let <var>mediaDevices</var> be <var>globalObject</var>'s <a =
data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacaptu=
re-main/#dfn-associated-mediadevices" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-d=
fn-associated-mediadevices-4">associated <code>MediaDevices<!---0.032930%--=
></code><!---0.032930%--></a>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
           <p>For each <var>source</var> in <var>mediaDevices</var>.<!---0.=
032930%--><a data-xref-type=3D"attribute" data-link-type=3D"attribute" data=
-link-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-xref-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-lt=3D"[[medi=
aStreamTrackSources]]" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn=
-mediastreamtracksources" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-mediastre=
amtracksources-3"><code>[[mediaStreamTrackSources<!---0.032930%-->]]<!---0.=
032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->,
           run the following sub steps:</p>
           <ol>
             <li>
               <p>If <var>source</var> is <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract=
-op" data-link-for=3D"source" data-xref-for=3D"source" href=3D"https://w3c.=
github.io/mediacapture-main/#source-stopped" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"re=
f-for-source-stopped-7">stopped<!---0.032930%--></a> or <a data-link-type=
=3D"dfn|abstract-op" data-link-for=3D"source" data-xref-for=3D"source" href=
=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-muted-0" class=3D"internal=
DFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-muted-0-3">muted<!---0.032930%--></a>, abort these s=
teps.</p>
             </li>
             <li>
               <p>Let <var>deviceId</var> be <var>source</var>'s device's d=
eviceId.</p>
             </li>
             <li>
               <p>If <var>mediaDevices</var>.<!---0.032930%--><a data-xref-=
type=3D"attribute" data-link-type=3D"attribute" data-link-for=3D"MediaDevic=
es" data-xref-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-lt=3D"[[devicesLiveMap]]" href=3D"h=
ttps://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-deviceslivemap" class=3D"intern=
alDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-deviceslivemap-4"><code>[[devicesLiveMap<!---0.032=
930%-->]]<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->[<var>deviceId</var>]=
 is
               <code>true</code>, return <code>true</code>.</p>
             </li>
           </ol>
         </li>
         <li>
           <p>Return <code>false</code>.</p>
         </li>
        </ol>
        <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-generatedID=
-18"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note-18" ari=
a-level=3D"5"><span>Note</span><!---0.032930%--></div><p class=3D"">This al=
gorithm covers all capture tracks, including microphone, camera and display=
.</p></div>
      </section>
    </section>
