nternalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-devicechangeevent-devices-7"><code>devices<!-=
--0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->
                that might happen from changes in device information exposu=
re.</p>
              </div></div>
              <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-gener=
atedID-20"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note-2=
