      the application to determine which constraints the <a data-link-type=
=3D"dfn|abstract-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-u=
ser-agent" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-user-agent-74">User Agen=
