ar>p</var> with value
                  <var>stream</var>, run the following step:</p>
                  <ol>
                    <li>
                      <p>Invoke <var>successCallback</var> with
                      <var>stream</var> as the argument.</p>
                    </li>
                  </ol>
                </li>
