te-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"upon-rejection" href=3D"https://webidl.spec.=
whatwg.org/#upon-rejection">Upon rejection<!---0.032930%--></a> of <var>p</=
var> with reason
                  <var>r</var>, run the following step:</p>
