am-103"><code>MediaStream<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> as d=
escribed
              in the failure steps of the <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-=
link-type=3D"interface" data-lt=3D"Navigator" data-cite=3D"html" data-cite-=
path=3D"/system-state.html" data-cite-frag=3D"navigator" href=3D"https://ht=
ml.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/system-state.html#navigator"><code>Navigator<!=
---0.032930%--></code></a>.<!---0.032930%--><a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-=
xref-type=3D"attribute|dict-member|const" data-link-for=3D"Navigator" data-=
xref-for=3D"Navigator" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom=
-navigator-getusermedia" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-navigator-=
getusermedia-6"><code>getUserMedia<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930=
%-->
              algorithm.
