  <section id=3D"examples"><!--OddPage--><div class=3D"header-wrapper"><h2 =
id=3D"x12-examples"><bdi class=3D"secno">12.<!---0.032930%--> </bdi>Example=
s</h2><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-mai=
n/#examples" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 12."></a></div>
   =20
    <div>
      <p>This sample code exposes a button. When clicked, the button is
      disabled and the user is prompted to offer a stream. The user can cau=
se
      the button to be re-enabled by providing a stream (e.g., giving the p=
age
      access to the local camera) and then disabling the stream (e.g., revo=
king
      that access).</p>
      <div class=3D"example" id=3D"example-14">
        <div class=3D"marker">
    <a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/=
#example-14">Example<!---0.032930%--><bdi> 14<!---0.032930%--></bdi></a><!-=
--0.032930%-->
  </div><!---0.032930%--> <pre aria-busy=3D"false"><code class=3D"hljs xml"=
><span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;<span class=3D"hljs-name">button</span> <span=
 class=3D"hljs-attr">id</span>=3D<span class=3D"hljs-string">"startBtn"</sp=
an>&gt;</span>Start<span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class=3D"hljs-name">=
button</span>&gt;</span>
<span class=3D"hljs-tag">&lt;<span class=3D"hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</s=
pan><span class=3D"language-javascript">
<span class=3D"hljs-keyword">const</span> startBtn =3D <span class=3D"hljs-=
variable language_">document</span>.<span class=3D"hljs-title function_">ge=
tElementById</span>(<span class=3D"hljs-string">'startBtn'</span>);

startBtn.<span class=3D"hljs-property">onclick</span> =3D <span class=3D"hl=
js-title function_">async</span> () =3D&gt; {
  <span class=3D"hljs-keyword">try</span> {
    startBtn.<span class=3D"hljs-property">disabled</span> =3D <span class=
=3D"hljs-literal">true</span>;
    <span class=3D"hljs-keyword">const</span> constraints =3D {
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">audio</span>: <span class=3D"hljs-literal">=
true</span>,
      <span class=3D"hljs-attr">video</span>: <span class=3D"hljs-literal">=
true</span>
    };

    <span class=3D"hljs-keyword">const</span> stream =3D <span class=3D"hlj=
s-keyword">await</span> navigator.<span class=3D"hljs-property">mediaDevice=
s</span>.<span class=3D"hljs-title function_">getUserMedia</span>(constrain=
ts);

    <span class=3D"hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class=3D"hljs-keyword">c=
onst</span> track <span class=3D"hljs-keyword">of</span> stream.<span class=
=3D"hljs-title function_">getTracks</span>()) {
      track.<span class=3D"hljs-property">onended</span> =3D <span class=3D=
"hljs-function">() =3D&gt;</span> {
        startBtn.<span class=3D"hljs-property">disabled</span> =3D stream.<=
span class=3D"hljs-title function_">getTracks</span>().<span class=3D"hljs-=
title function_">some</span>(<span class=3D"hljs-function">(<span class=3D"=
hljs-params">t</span>) =3D&gt;</span> t.<span class=3D"hljs-property">ready=
State</span> =3D=3D <span class=3D"hljs-string">'live'</span>);
      };
    }
