  <section id=3D"permissions-integration-0"><!--OddPage--><div class=3D"hea=
der-wrapper"><h2 id=3D"permissions-integration"><bdi class=3D"secno">13.<!-=
--0.032930%--> </bdi>Permissions Integration</h2><a class=3D"self-link" hre=
f=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#permissions-integration" aria=
-label=3D"Permalink for Section 13."></a></div>
   =20
    <p>This specification defines two <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=
=3D"permissions" data-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"dfn-powerful-feature=
" href=3D"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions/#dfn-powerful-feature">powerful=
 features<!---0.032930%--></a> identified by the
    <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-link-for=3D"powerful feature" data-xref-=
for=3D"powerful feature" data-cite=3D"permissions" data-cite-path=3D"" data=
-cite-frag=3D"dfn-name" href=3D"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions/#dfn-name=
">names<!---0.032930%--></a> <code><dfn class=3D"permission" data-dfn-type=
=3D"permission" id=3D"dfn-camera" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog" d=
ata-export=3D"">"camera"</dfn></code> and <code><dfn class=3D"permission" d=
ata-dfn-type=3D"permission" id=3D"dfn-microphone" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspo=
pup=3D"dialog" data-export=3D"">"microphone"</dfn></code>.</p>
    <p>It defines the following types and algorithms:</p>
    <dl>
      <dt>
        <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-link-for=3D"powerful feature" data-x=
ref-for=3D"powerful feature" data-cite=3D"permissions" data-cite-path=3D"" =
data-cite-frag=3D"dfn-permission-descriptor-type" href=3D"https://www.w3.or=
g/TR/permissions/#dfn-permission-descriptor-type">permission descriptor typ=
e<!---0.032930%--></a>
      </dt>
      <dd>
        <pre class=3D"idl def" id=3D"webidl-1877239468"><span class=3D"idlH=
eader"><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-ma=
in/#webidl-1877239468">WebIDL</a><button title=3D"Copy IDL to clipboard" cl=
ass=3D"respec-button-copy-paste removeOnSave"><svg height=3D"16" viewBox=3D=
"0 0 14 16" width=3D"14"><path fill-rule=3D"evenodd" d=3D"M2 13h4v1H2v-1zm5=
-6H2v1h5V7zm2 3V8l-3 3 3 3v-2h5v-2H9zM4.5 9H2v1h2.5V9zM2 12h2.5v-1H2v1zm9 1=
h1v2c-.02.28-.11.52-.3.7-.19.18-.42.28-.7.3H1c-.55 0-1-.45-1-1V4c0-.55.45-1=
 1-1h3c0-1.11.89-2 2-2 1.11 0 2 .89 2 2h3c.55 0 1 .45 1 1v5h-1V6H1v9h10v-2z=
M2 5h8c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H8c-.55 0-1-.45-1-1s-.45-1-1-1-1 .45-1 1-.45 1-1 1H3c=
-.55 0-1 .45-1 1z"></path></svg></button></span><code><span data-idl=3D"" c=
lass=3D"idlDictionary" id=3D"idl-def-cameradevicepermissiondescriptor" data=
-title=3D"CameraDevicePermissionDescriptor">dictionary <dfn data-export=3D"=
" data-dfn-type=3D"dictionary" id=3D"dom-cameradevicepermissiondescriptor" =
data-idl=3D"dictionary" data-title=3D"CameraDevicePermissionDescriptor" dat=
a-dfn-for=3D"" class=3D"idlID" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog"><cod=
e>CameraDevicePermissionDescriptor<!---0.032930%--></code></dfn> : <span cl=
ass=3D"idlSuperclass"><a data-link-type=3D"dictionary" data-xref-type=3D"_I=
DL_" data-cite=3D"permissions" data-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"dom-pe=
rmissiondescriptor" href=3D"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions/#dom-permissi=
ondescriptor">PermissionDescriptor<!---0.032930%--></a><!---0.032930%--></s=
pan> {<span data-idl=3D"" class=3D"idlMember" id=3D"idl-def-cameradeviceper=
missiondescriptor-pantiltzoom" data-title=3D"panTiltZoom" data-dfn-for=3D"C=
ameraDevicePermissionDescriptor"><span class=3D"idlType">
  <a data-link-type=3D"interface" data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-cite=3D"web=
idl" data-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"idl-boolean" href=3D"https://web=
idl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-boolean">boolean<!---0.032930%--></a><!---0.032930=
%--></span> <dfn data-export=3D"" data-dfn-type=3D"dict-member" id=3D"dom-c=
ameradevicepermissiondescriptor-pantiltzoom" data-idl=3D"field" data-title=
=3D"panTiltZoom" data-dfn-for=3D"CameraDevicePermissionDescriptor" data-typ=
e=3D"boolean" class=3D"idlName" tabindex=3D"0" aria-haspopup=3D"dialog"><co=
de>panTiltZoom<!---0.032930%--></code></dfn> =3D false;<!---0.032930%--></s=
pan>
};<!---0.032930%--></span><!---0.032930%--></code></pre>
        <p>
          A permission covers access to at least one device of a kind.
        </p>
        <p>
          The semantics of the descriptor is that it queries for access to =
any device of that kind.
          Thus, if a query
          for the <a href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-c=
amera" class=3D"internalDFN" data-link-type=3D"dfn" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-camer=
a-5"><code>"camera"</code></a> permission returns "<a data-link-type=3D"enu=
m-value" data-xref-type=3D"enum-value" data-link-for=3D"PermissionState" da=
ta-xref-for=3D"PermissionState" data-cite=3D"permissions" data-cite-path=3D=
"" data-cite-frag=3D"dom-permissionstate-granted" href=3D"https://www.w3.or=
g/TR/permissions/#dom-permissionstate-granted"><code>granted<!---0.032930%-=
-></code></a>"<!---0.032930%-->, the
          client knows that it will get access to one camera without a perm=
ission prompt, and if
          "<a data-link-type=3D"enum-value" data-xref-type=3D"enum-value" d=
ata-link-for=3D"PermissionState" data-xref-for=3D"PermissionState" data-cit=
e=3D"permissions" data-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"dom-permissionstate=
-denied" href=3D"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions/#dom-permissionstate-den=
ied"><code>denied<!---0.032930%--></code></a>"<!---0.032930%--> is returned=
, it knows that no getUserMedia request for a
          camera will succeed.
        </p>
        <p>
          If the User Agent considers permission given to some, but not all=
, devices of a kind, a query
          will return
          "<a data-link-type=3D"enum-value" data-xref-type=3D"enum-value" d=
ata-link-for=3D"PermissionState" data-xref-for=3D"PermissionState" data-cit=
e=3D"permissions" data-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"dom-permissionstate=
-granted" href=3D"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions/#dom-permissionstate-gr=
anted"><code>granted<!---0.032930%--></code></a>"<!---0.032930%-->.
        </p>
        <p>
          If the User Agent considers permission denied to all devices of a=
 kind, a query
          will return
          "<a data-link-type=3D"enum-value" data-xref-type=3D"enum-value" d=
ata-link-for=3D"PermissionState" data-xref-for=3D"PermissionState" data-cit=
e=3D"permissions" data-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"dom-permissionstate=
-denied" href=3D"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions/#dom-permissionstate-den=
ied"><code>denied<!---0.032930%--></code></a>"<!---0.032930%-->.
        </p>
        <p>
          <code>{name: "camera", panTiltZoom: true}<!---0.032930%--></code>=
 is <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-link-for=3D"PermissionDescriptor" data-x=
ref-for=3D"PermissionDescriptor" data-cite=3D"permissions" data-cite-path=
=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"dfn-stronger-than" href=3D"https://www.w3.org/TR/pe=
rmissions/#dfn-stronger-than">stronger than<!---0.032930%--></a>
          <code>{name: "camera", panTiltZoom: false}<!---0.032930%--></code=
>.
        </p>
        <div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-generatedID=
-35"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note-35" ari=
a-level=3D"3"><span>Note</span><!---0.032930%--></div><p class=3D"">
          A "<a data-link-type=3D"enum-value" data-xref-type=3D"enum-value"=
 data-link-for=3D"PermissionState" data-xref-for=3D"PermissionState" data-c=
ite=3D"permissions" data-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"dom-permissionsta=
te-granted" href=3D"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions/#dom-permissionstate-=
granted"><code>granted<!---0.032930%--></code></a>"<!---0.032930%--> permis=
sion is no guarantee that getUserMedia will succeed. It
          only indicates that the user will not be prompted for permission.=
 There are many
          other things (such as constraints or the camera being in use) tha=
t can cause
          getUserMedia to fail.
        </p></div>
      </dd>
      <dt>
        <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-link-for=3D"powerful feature" data-x=
ref-for=3D"powerful feature" data-cite=3D"permissions" data-cite-path=3D"" =
data-cite-frag=3D"dfn-permission-revocation-algorithm" href=3D"https://www.=
w3.org/TR/permissions/#dfn-permission-revocation-algorithm">permission revo=
cation algorithm<!---0.032930%--></a>
      </dt>
      <dd>
        This is the result of calling the <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract=
-op" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-device-permission=
-revocation-algorithm" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-device-permi=
ssion-revocation-algorithm-1">device permission revocation algorithm<!---0.=
032930%--></a> passing
        <!---0.032930%--><a data-link-type=3D"dict-member" data-xref-type=
=3D"attribute|dict-member|const" data-link-for=3D"PermissionDescriptor" dat=
a-xref-for=3D"PermissionDescriptor" data-cite=3D"permissions" data-cite-pat=
h=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"dom-permissiondescriptor-name" href=3D"https://www=
.w3.org/TR/permissions/#dom-permissiondescriptor-name"><code>name<!---0.032=
930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> as argument.
      </dd>
    </dl>
  </section>
  <section id=3D"permissions-policy-integration-0"><!--OddPage--><div class=
=3D"header-wrapper"><h2 id=3D"permissions-policy-integration"><bdi class=3D=
"secno">14.<!---0.032930%--> </bdi>Permissions Policy Integration</h2><a cl=
ass=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#permissi=
ons-policy-integration" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Section 14."></a></div>
   =20
    <p>This specification defines two <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=
=3D"permissions-policy" data-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"policy-contro=
lled-feature" href=3D"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions-policy-1/#policy-co=
ntrolled-feature">policy-controlled features<!---0.032930%--></a>
    identified by the strings <a href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture=
-main/#dfn-camera" class=3D"internalDFN" data-link-type=3D"dfn" id=3D"ref-f=
or-dfn-camera-6"><code>"camera"</code></a> and <a href=3D"https://w3c.githu=
b.io/mediacapture-main/#dfn-microphone" class=3D"internalDFN" data-link-typ=
e=3D"dfn" id=3D"ref-for-dfn-microphone-5"><code>"microphone"</code></a>.
    Both have a <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-link-for=3D"policy-controlle=
d feature" data-xref-for=3D"policy-controlled feature" data-cite=3D"permiss=
ions-policy" data-cite-path=3D"" data-cite-frag=3D"policy-controlled-featur=
e-default-allowlist" href=3D"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions-policy-1/#po=
licy-controlled-feature-default-allowlist">default allowlist<!---0.032930%-=
-></a> of
    <code class=3D"permissionspolicy">"self"</code>.
    </p><div class=3D"note" role=3D"note" id=3D"issue-container-generatedID=
-36"><div role=3D"heading" class=3D"note-title marker" id=3D"h-note-36" ari=
a-level=3D"3"><span>Note</span><!---0.032930%--></div><div class=3D"">
      <p>A <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" data-cite=3D"dom" data-cite-path=3D"" =
data-cite-frag=3D"concept-document" href=3D"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#co=
ncept-document">document<!---0.032930%--></a>'s <a data-link-type=3D"dfn" d=
ata-link-for=3D"Document" data-xref-for=3D"Document" data-cite=3D"html" dat=
a-cite-path=3D"/dom.html" data-cite-frag=3D"concept-document-permissions-po=
licy" href=3D"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/dom.html#concept-docum=
ent-permissions-policy">permissions policy<!---0.032930%--></a>
      determines whether any content in that document is allowed to use
      <!---0.032930%--><a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-xref-type=3D"attribut=
e|dict-member|const" data-link-for=3D"MediaDevices" data-xref-for=3D"MediaD=
evices" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediadevices-g=
etusermedia" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediadevices-getuserme=
dia-35"><code>getUserMedia<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> to =
request camera or microphone respectively. If
      disabled in any document, no content in the document will be <a data-=
