ediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-media=
streamtrack" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamtrack-125">=
<code>MediaStreamTrack<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> interfa=
ce,</li>
