eams-in-media-elements" class=3D"sec-ref"><bdi class=3D"secno">6. </bdi>Med=
iaStreams in Media Elements</a>), including
          adding a corollary to <a data-link-type=3D"dfn|abstract-op" data-=
link-for=3D"stream" data-xref-for=3D"stream" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/=
mediacapture-main/#stream-audible" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-stre=
am-audible-4">audible<!---0.032930%--></a>/inaudible
          for the new media type,
        </li>
        <li>updating <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" dat=
a-lt=3D"MediaDeviceKind" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#d=
om-mediadevicekind" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediadevicekind=
-6"><code>MediaDeviceKind<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%--> if t=
he new type has
        enumerable devices,</li>
        <li>updating the <!---0.032930%--><a data-link-type=3D"idl" data-xr=
ef-type=3D"method" data-link-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" data-xref-for=3D"Medi=
aStreamTrack" data-lt=3D"getCapabilities()" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/m=
