        <li>describing any new security and/or privacy considerations (see
        <a href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#privacy-and-sec=
urity-considerations" class=3D"sec-ref"><bdi class=3D"secno">16. </bdi>Priv=
