data-xref-type=3D"attribute|dict-member|const" data-link-for=3D"MediaStream=
Track" data-xref-for=3D"MediaStreamTrack" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/med=
iacapture-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack-kind" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-=
for-dom-mediastreamtrack-kind-6"><code>kind<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!--=
