    <section id=3D"defining-a-new-constrainable-property"><div class=3D"hea=
der-wrapper"><h3 id=3D"x17-2-defining-a-new-constrainable-property"><bdi cl=
ass=3D"secno">17.2<!---0.032930%--> </bdi>Defining a new constrainable prop=
erty</h3><a class=3D"self-link" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-=
main/#defining-a-new-constrainable-property" aria-label=3D"Permalink for Se=
ction 17.2"></a></div>
     =20
      <p>This will require thinking through and defining how Constraints,
      Capabilities, and Settings for the property (see <a href=3D"https://w=
3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#terminology" class=3D"sec-ref"><bdi class=
=3D"secno">3. </bdi>Terminology</a>) will work. The relevant text in
      <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaTr=
ackSupportedConstraints" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#d=
om-mediatracksupportedconstraints" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-=
mediatracksupportedconstraints-6"><code>MediaTrackSupportedConstraints<!---=
0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->,
      <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaTr=
ackCapabilities" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-media=
trackcapabilities" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediatrackcapabi=
lities-8"><code>MediaTrackCapabilities<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.03=
2930%-->,
      <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaTr=
ackConstraints" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediat=
rackconstraints" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediatrackconstrai=
nts-9"><code>MediaTrackConstraints<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930=
%-->,
      <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaTr=
ackSettings" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediatrac=
ksettings" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediatracksettings-8"><c=
ode>MediaTrackSettings<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.032930%-->, <a hre=
f=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#constrainable-properties" cla=
ss=3D"sec-ref"><bdi class=3D"secno">4.3.8 </bdi>Constrainable Properties</a=
>, and
      <a data-xref-type=3D"_IDL_" data-link-type=3D"idl" data-lt=3D"MediaSt=
reamConstraints" href=3D"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-media=
streamconstraints" class=3D"internalDFN" id=3D"ref-for-dom-mediastreamconst=
raints-9"><code>MediaStreamConstraints<!---0.032930%--></code></a><!---0.03=
2930%--> are the model to use.</p>
      <p>Creators of extension specifications are strongly encouraged to no=
tify
      the specification maintainers on <a href=3D"https://github.com/w3c/me=
diacapture-main/issues">the specification repository</a>.<br>
      Future versions of this specification and others created by the WebRT=
C Working Group will take into consideration all extensions they are
      aware of in an attempt to reduce potential usage conflicts.</p>
    </section>
